{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}About Us - GameHub{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
<style>
    .about-wrapper {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 2rem auto;
        padding: 2rem;
        color: #f1f1f1;
        text-align: left;
    }

    .about-wrapper h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    .about-wrapper p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
</style>

<div class="about-wrapper">
    <h1>About GameHub</h1>
    <p>
        Welcome to <strong>GameHub</strong>, your ultimate destination for discovering, buying, and reviewing the best video games across all platforms.
        Our mission is to bring gamers together by offering a rich library of games, detailed reviews, and a seamless shopping experience.
    </p>
    <p>
        Whether you're into action, adventure, RPGs, or indie gems, GameHub is designed to help you find your next favorite game.
        We're passionate about gaming and committed to building a community where both casual players and hardcore fans can thrive.
    </p>
    <p>
        GameHub is developed as part of a Symfony web application project, aiming to demonstrate solid e-commerce features including
        product browsing, user reviews, secure checkout, and personalized recommendations.
    </p>
    <p>
        Thank you for visiting, and happy gaming!
    </p>
</div>
{% endblock %}
